{"type":"message","id":"4c6021a1","parentId":"6a7afec5","timestamp":"2026-03-04T17:38:35.229Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"扫码后 MCP 还是显示未登录，但浏览器已经登录了，可能是 cookie 路径配置问题，先跳过登录测试直接用其他工具看看能不能正常工作。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"头儿，browser 里登录成功了，但 xiaohongshu-mcp 服务用的是独立的 cookie 文件，跟浏览器不互通。\n\n我看看能不能找到 mcp 的 cookie 文件位置，或者直接用 browser 方式测试长文、通知、评论这三个功能。你选哪个？\n\n我建议直接用 browser 测，快一点，还能看到界面。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":56866,"output":151,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57017,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772645911773}}
