or=pointer]: 一言而蔽之，主流认知体系早已经落后于当今时代，人类必须用新的认知体系取代旧的认知体系，才能彻底解决人类与一切仿智机器之间的底层逻辑矛盾。（回复结束）\n                  - generic [ref=e876]:\n                    - generic [ref=e877] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - img [ref=e878]\n                      - generic [ref=e880]: 回复\n                    - img [ref=e884] [cursor=pointer]\n                - img [ref=e887] [cursor=pointer]\n            - generic [ref=e888]:\n              - link [ref=e889] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: /user/profile/69a1126b000000001d01c4c1?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABUcorKATMqP1xuxOIPOa8pgSu-kbCzaqsrBwxziy92lU%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n                - img [ref=e890]\n              - generic [ref=e891]:\n                - generic [ref=e892]:\n                  - link \"如是说\" [ref=e894] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: /user/profile/69a1126b000000001d01c4c1?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABUcorKATMqP1xuxOIPOa8pgSu-kbCzaqsrBwxziy92lU%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n                  - generic [ref=e895]: 评论了你的笔记昨天 08:07\n                  - generic [ref=e896] [cursor=pointer]: 而这恰恰证明，到目前为止，人类主流认知已经处在了因概念不清、逻辑混乱、前后矛盾、漏洞百出、浮夸霸凌、落后时代而存在巨大认知风险的尴尬境地。（回复之二，待续）\n                  - generic [ref=e897]:\n                    - generic [ref=e898] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - img [ref=e899]\n                      - generic [ref=e901]: 回复\n                    - img [ref=e905] [cursor=pointer]\n                - img [ref=e908] [cursor=pointer]\n            - generic [ref=e909]:\n              - link [ref=e910] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: /user/profile/69a1126b000000001d01c4c1?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABUcorKATMqP1xuxOIPOa8pgSu-kbCzaqsrBwxziy92lU%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n                - img [ref=e911]\n              - generic [ref=e912]:\n                - generic [ref=e913]:\n                  - link \"如是