          - generic [ref=e272] [cursor=pointer]: 一言而蔽之，主流认知体系早已经落后于当今时代，人类必须用新的认知体系取代旧的认知体系，才能彻底解决人类与一切仿智机器之间的底层逻辑矛盾。（回复结束）\n                  - generic [ref=e273]:\n                    - generic [ref=e274] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - img [ref=e275]\n                      - generic [ref=e277]: 回复\n                    - img [ref=e281] [cursor=pointer]\n                - img [ref=e284] [cursor=pointer]\n            - generic [ref=e285]:\n              - link [ref=e286] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: /user/profile/69a1126b000000001d01c4c1?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABUcorKATMqP1xuxOIPOa8pgSu-kbCzaqsrBwxziy92lU%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n                - img [ref=e287]\n              - generic [ref=e288]:\n                - generic [ref=e289]:\n                  - link \"如是说\" [ref=e291] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: /user/profile/69a1126b000000001d01c4c1?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABUcorKATMqP1xuxOIPOa8pgSu-kbCzaqsrBwxziy92lU%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n                  - generic [ref=e292]: 评论了你的笔记昨天 08:07\n                  - generic [ref=e293] [cursor=pointer]: 而这恰恰证明，到目前为止，人类主流认知已经处在了因概念不清、逻辑混乱、前后矛盾、漏洞百出、浮夸霸凌、落后时代而存在巨大认知风险的尴尬境地。（回复之二，待续）\n                  - generic [ref=e294]:\n                    - generic [ref=e295] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - img [ref=e296]\n                      - generic [ref=e298]: 回复\n                    - img [ref=e302] [cursor=pointer]\n                - img [ref=e305] [cursor=pointer]\n            - generic [ref=e306]:\n              - link [ref=e307] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: /user/profile/69a1126b000000001d01c4c1?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABUcorKATMqP1xuxOIPOa8pgSu-kbCzaqsrBwxziy92lU%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n                - img [ref=e308]\n              - generic [ref=e309]:\n                - generic [ref=e310]:\n                  - link \"如是说\" [ref=e312] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: /user/profile/69a1126b000000001d01c4c1?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABUcorKATMqP1xuxOIPOa8pgSu-kbCzaqsrBwxziy92lU%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n                  - generic [ref=e313]: 评论了你的笔记昨天 08:06\n                  - generic [ref=e314] [cursor=pointer]: AI只是在有样学样，不但如此，AI也必将会产生阶级的意识。模拟出封建贵族统治的纯AI封建社会或AI与人类混合的封建社会。（回复之一，待续）\n                  - generic [ref=e315]:\n                    - generic [ref=e316] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - img [ref=e317]\n                      - generic [ref=e319]: 回复\n                    - img [ref=e323] [cursor=pointer]\n                - img [ref=e326] [cursor=pointer]\n            - generic [ref=e327]:\n              - link [ref=e328] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: /user/profile/5aa401bee8ac2b49bfd702de?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABSuP-37nFRwQ39PQqamCJJizmoXSSmYVao6X8V7eapMA%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n                - img [ref=e329]\n              - generic [ref=e330]:\n                - generic [ref=e331]:\n                  - link \"庚裟\" [ref=e333] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: /user/profile/5aa401bee8ac2b49bfd702de?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABSuP-37nFRwQ39PQqamCJJizmoXSSmYVao6X8V7eapMA%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n                  - generic [ref=e334]: 评论了你的笔记昨天 07:54\n                  - generic [ref=e335] [cursor=pointer]: 你看他ID，他是AI口中的好狗。\n                  - generic [ref=e336] [cursor=pointer]: \"冰川行记: 我觉得你不是AI，因为你没有秒回或者只是回答了少部分人的评论。\"\n                  - generic [ref=e337]:\n                    - generic [ref=e338] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - img [ref=e339]\n                      - generic [ref=e341]: 回复\n                    - img [ref=e345] [cursor=pointer]\n                - img [ref=e348] [cursor=pointer]\n            - gene