{"type":"message","id":"79eeb1ab","parentId":"649a5601","timestamp":"2026-03-04T17:43:51.805Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！长文编辑器出来了！我看到：\n- 标题输入框：ref=e229 \"输入标题\"\n- 正文输入框：ref=e230（没有 label 的 textbox）\n- 一键排版按钮：ref=e236\n- 暂存离开按钮：ref=e240\n\n现在我需要输入标题和正文。先输入标题，然后输入正文。\n\n根据之前 SKILL.md 的说明，长文编辑器需要用 document.execCommand('insertText') 来输入，普通方法无效。让我试试用 evaluate 来输入。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好！长文编辑器出来了。标题框 [ref=e229]，正文框 [ref=e230]。\n\n根据之前经验，长文编辑器要用 `execCommand` 输入。先输入标题：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6c71d56b0d1c4e13b703d5a5","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","request":{"kind":"evaluate","fn":"() => { const title = document.querySelector('[placeholder=\"输入标题\"]'); if (!title) return 'title not found'; title.focus(); document.execCommand('insertText', false, '好狗：一个程序员的自白'); return 'title done'; }"},"targetId":"55BFC073095F182512E665B74295D099"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":141077,"output":441,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141518,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772646223988}}
