{"type":"message","id":"f99abc20","parentId":"4533b47a","timestamp":"2026-03-04T17:45:25.348Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"头儿说必须用 MCP 实现，不能用 browser。但之前 xiaohongshu-mcp 服务一直显示未登录，cookie 和浏览器不互通。\n\n让我再试试检查 MCP 的登录状态，看看是不是现在能用了。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了，头儿！不用 browser，纯用 MCP。让我关掉浏览器 tab，然后用 MCP 方式测试。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-7ff1add0093b43428ea9b94fbbdfe0ae","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"close","targetId":"55BFC073095F182512E665B74295D099"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":125486,"output":157,"cacheRead":1535,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127178,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772646306322}}
