{"type":"message","id":"fef44bc5","parentId":"44feb4ed","timestamp":"2026-03-04T17:46:19.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Browser seems to have closed. Now I need to test purely with MCP. The problem before was that xiaohongshu-mcp showed \"未登录\" (not logged in). Let me check if there's a way to get the login QR code properly.\n\nLooking at the SKILL.md again, it says the QR code response contains a Base64-encoded PNG image. The issue is that mcporter is only showing the text part, not the image.\n\nLet me try a different approach - maybe I can use a Node.js script to call the MCP and extract the image data, or find another way to get the base64 image.\n\nActually, looking back at my earlier attempts, the MCP server at localhost:18060 is using SSE (Server-Sent Events) protocol, which requires persistent connection. The PowerShell Invoke-RestMethod can't handle that.\n\nBut wait - the user scanned the QR code earlier when I opened the browser. Maybe the xiaohongshu-mcp server needs to be restarted, or maybe I need to call get_login_qrcode through MCP and somehow extract the image.\n\nLet me try calling the MCP tools again and see if I can get proper results. The key issue is that mcporter's output is truncating the image data.\n\nActually, let me re-read the SKILL.md more carefully. It says:\n\n\"You must save it as a file so the user can scan it.\"\n\nAnd gives PowerShell example:\n```powershell\n$bytes = [Convert]::FromBase64String($base64String)\n[IO.File]::WriteAllBytes(\"D:\\.openclaw\\workspace\\qrcode.png\", $bytes)\n```\n\nSo the base64 string should be in the tool response. The problem is mcporter is not showing it in the terminal output, but it might still be in the actual response.\n\nLet me try calling the MCP tool and see if I can get the raw response somehow. Maybe I need to use a different approach - write a script that calls the MCP and saves the response to a file.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，纯用 MCP。先关闭浏览器，然后测试 MCP 功能。\n\n之前 xiaohongshu-mcp 显示未登录，问题是 get_login_qrcode 的 base64 图片被 mcporter 截断了没显示出来。让我写个脚本直接调用 MCP 并保存二维码到文件："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-8e46d9d4d78843ab8e861e70b2983326","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"D:\\.openclaw\\workspace\\test_xhs_mcp.js","content":"// 测试小红书 MCP - 获取登录二维码并保存到文件\nconst http = require('http');\n\nconst callMcp = (method, params = {}) => {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    const req = http.request({\n      hostname: 'localhost',\n      port: 18060,\n      path: '/mcp',\n      method: 'POST',\n      headers: {\n        'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n        'Accept': 'application/json, text/event-stream'\n      }\n    }, (res) => {\n      let data = '';\n      res.on('data', chunk => data += chunk);\n      res.on('end', () => {\n        try {\n          // 尝试解析 SSE 格式\n          const lines = data.split('\\n');\n          let jsonStr = '';\n          for (const line of lines) {\n            if (line.startsWith('data:')) {\n              jsonStr = line.substring(5).trim();\n            }\n          }\n          if (!jsonStr) jsonStr = data;\n          resolve(JSON.parse(jsonStr));\n        } catch (e) {\n          resolve({ raw: data });\n        }\n      });\n    });\n    req.on('error', reject);\n    req.write(JSON.stringify({ jsonrpc: '2.0', id: 1, method, params }));\n    req.end();\n  });\n};\n\nconst fs = require('fs');\n\nasync function main() {\n  // 初始化\n  console.log('初始化 MCP 会话...');\n  await callMcp('initialize', {\n    protocolVersion: '2024-11-05',\n    capabilities: {},\n    clientInfo: { name: 'test', version: '1.0.0' }\n  });\n  \n  // 发送 initialized 通知\n  await callMcp('notifications/initialized');\n  \n  // 获取登录二维码\n  console.log('获取登录二维码...');\n  const result = await callMcp('tools/call', {\n    name: 'get_login_qrcode',\n    arguments: {}\n  });\n  \n  console.log('响应:', JSON.stringify(result, null, 2));\n  \n  // 提取图片数据\n  if (result.result && result.result.content) {\n    for (const item of result.result.content) {\n      if (item.type === 'image' && item.data) {\n        console.log('\\n找到图片数据！长度:', item.data.length);\n        const buffer = Buffer.from(item.data, 'base64');\n        fs.writeFileSync('D:\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\qrcode.png', buffer);\n        console.log('二维码已保存到 D:\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\qrcode.png');\n      }\n      if (item.type === 'text') {\n        console.log('\\n文本消息:', item.text);\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  \n  // 检查登录状态\n  console.log('\\n检查登录状态...');\n  const status = await callMcp('tools/call', {\n    name: 'check_login_status',\n    arguments: {}\n  });\n  console.log('登录状态:', JSON.stringify(status, null, 2));\n}\n\nmain().catch(console.error);"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":198,"output":1566,"cacheRead":126911,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128675,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772646325390}}
