{"type":"message","id":"bafa870d","parentId":"711d6193","timestamp":"2026-03-04T17:46:57.101Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题是 SSE 协议需要持久连接，简单的 HTTP 请求无法处理。让我想想其他方法。\n\n实际上，xiaohongshu-mcp 是一个独立运行的 MCP 服务器，它使用的是 HTTP + SSE 协议。我需要找到一种方式来正确调用它。\n\n或者，我可以直接使用 mcporter，但需要找到一种方式来获取完整的响应数据，包括 base64 图片。\n\n让我试试用 mcporter 的其他参数或者看看能不能把输出重定向到文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"脚本写好了，但 SSE 协议比较复杂。让我换个思路——直接用 mcporter 但把输出保存到文件："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-cf0a7c28741b4c9db5b4629f9c66afc8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"npx mcporter call xiaohongshu-mcp.get_login_qrcode 2>&1 | Out-File -FilePath \"D:\\.openclaw\\workspace\\mcp_output.txt\" -Encoding utf8; Get-Content \"D:\\.openclaw\\workspace\\mcp_output.txt\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":128436,"output":302,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128738,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772646379481}}
