{"type":"message","id":"df69f563","parentId":"e5030699","timestamp":"2026-03-04T17:49:28.745Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"MCP 服务启动成功了，check_login_status 返回未登录。现在我需要获取登录二维码，问题是 mcporter 把 base64 图片截断了没显示。\n\n让我写个简单的脚本，用 HTTP 直接调用 MCP 并把 base64 图片保存到文件：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"MCP 服务启动了，但未登录。我写个脚本直接调用 MCP 并保存二维码到文件："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-6a71395046664337b4e0b988efa78f18","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$ErrorActionPreference = 'Continue'\n$headers = @{Accept='application/json,text/event-stream'}\n\n# 初始化会话\n$body = '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":0,\"method\":\"initialize\",\"params\":{\"protocolVersion\":\"2024-11-05\",\"capabilities\":{},\"clientInfo\":{\"name\":\"test\",\"version\":\"1.0.0\"}}}'\n$null = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri 'http://localhost:18060/mcp' -Method Post -ContentType 'application/json' -Headers $headers -Body $body -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n\n# 发送 initialized 通知\n$null = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri 'http://localhost:18060/mcp' -Method Post -ContentType 'application/json' -Headers $headers -Body '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"notifications/initialized\"}' -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n\n# 获取二维码 - 用 Invoke-WebRequest 获取原始响应\n$resp = Invoke-WebRequest -Uri 'http://localhost:18060/mcp' -Method Post -ContentType 'application/json' -Headers $headers -Body '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"method\":\"tools/call\",\"params\":{\"name\":\"get_login_qrcode\",\"arguments\":{}}}' -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n\n# 保存原始响应到文件\n$resp.Content | Out-File -FilePath \"D:\\.openclaw\\workspace\\mcp_raw.txt\" -Encoding utf8\nWrite-Host \"原始响应已保存到 D:\\.openclaw\\workspace\\mcp_raw.txt\"\n\n# 尝试解析并提取图片\ntry {\n  $json = $resp.Content | ConvertFrom-Json\n  if ($json.result.content) {\n    foreach ($item in $json.result.content) {\n      if ($item.type -eq 'image' -and $item.data) {\n        Write-Host \"找到图片数据，长度: $($item.data.Length)\"\n        $bytes = [Convert]::FromBase64String($item.data)\n        [IO.File]::WriteAllBytes(\"D:\\.openclaw\\workspace\\qrcode.png\", $bytes)\n        Write-Host \"二维码已保存到 D:\\.openclaw\\workspace\\qrcode.png\"\n      }\n      if ($item.type -eq 'text') {\n        Write-Host \"文本: $($item.text)\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n} catch {\n  Write-Host \"解析错误: $_\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":126666,"output":648,"cacheRead":2111,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129425,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772646529487}}
