{"type":"message","id":"92f27729","parentId":"75d6ce47","timestamp":"2026-03-04T17:52:43.165Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"初始化成功了！但连接在发送初始化后就关闭了，因为这是 HTTP 请求，不是持久的 SSE 连接。\n\nMCP 的 SSE 协议需要保持连接。问题是：\n1. HTTP 请求发送后就关闭了\n2. 需要在同一个连接里发送 initialized 通知和 tools/call\n\n让我试试在一个请求里发送多个消息，或者用 EventSource 来保持连接。\n\n不过，我现在想到另一个方法——xiaohongshu-mcp 可能也支持 JSON-RPC over HTTP（非 SSE），让我试试看直接发送请求，不用 SSE。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"初始化成功了，但连接关闭了。SSE 需要保持连接。\n\n让我试试直接发送一个完整请求（包含 initialized 和 tools/call）："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-2cb3bc9c56444e9ba9c41348c178bc40","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"const http = require('http');\nconst fs = require('fs');\n\nasync function main() {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    const req = http.request({\n      hostname: 'localhost', port: 18060, path: '/mcp', method: 'POST',\n      headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json', 'Accept': 'application/json, text/event-stream' }\n    }, res => {\n      let buffer = '';\n      res.on('data', chunk => buffer += chunk);\n      res.on('end', () => {\n        console.log('完整响应:\\n', buffer);\n        const lines = buffer.split('\\n');\n        for (const line of lines) {\n          if (line.startsWith('data:')) {\n            try {\n              const json = JSON.parse(line.slice(5).trim());\n              if (json.result?.content) {\n                for (const c of json.result.content) {\n                  if (c.type === 'image' && c.data) {\n                    fs.writeFileSync('D:/.openclaw/workspace/qrcode.png', Buffer.from(c.data, 'base64'));\n                    console.log('\\n✅ 二维码已保存到 D:/.openclaw/workspace/qrcode.png');\n                  }\n                  if (c.type === 'text') console.log('文本:', c.text);\n                }\n              }\n            } catch(e) {}\n          }\n        }\n        resolve();\n      });\n    });\n    req.on('error', reject);\n    \n    // 发送批量请求：initialize + initialized + tools/call\n    console.log('发送批量请求...');\n    const batch = [\n      {jsonrpc:'2.0',id:0,method:'initialize',params:{protocolVersion:'2024-11-05',capabilities:{},clientInfo:{name:'test',version:'1.0'}}},\n      {jsonrpc:'2.0',method:'notifications/initialized'},\n      {jsonrpc:'2.0',id:1,method:'tools/call',params:{name:'get_login_qrcode',arguments:{}}}\n    ];\n    req.write(JSON.stringify(batch));\n    req.end();\n  });\n}\n\nmain().catch(e => console.error('错误:', e));","path":"D:\\.openclaw\\workspace\\get_qrcode5.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":246,"output":753,"cacheRead":127551,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128550,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772646729453}}
