{"type":"message","id":"c8d73167","parentId":"f940884b","timestamp":"2026-03-04T17:53:02.599Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我暂停，我需要用 MCP 方式测试小红书的长文、通知、评论三个功能。\n\n之前的问题是：\n1. get_login_qrcode 返回的 base64 图片被 mcporter 截断了\n2. 我尝试用 Node.js 直接调用 MCP，但 SSE 协议比较复杂\n\n让我换个思路——我之前已经用 browser 扫码登录了小红书网页版，现在检查一下 xiaohongshu-mcp 的登录状态，看看是否已经登录成功。\n\n如果已经登录，我就可以直接测试 MCP 的三个功能：\n1. publish_longform - 发布长文\n2. get_notification_comments - 获取通知评论\n3. post_comment_to_feed - 发表评论","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我先检查一下 MCP 的登录状态："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-cb2a34d6f5e64ed69b91016051f4522c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"npx mcporter call xiaohongshu-mcp.check_login_status"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":122990,"output":329,"cacheRead":2111,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125430,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772646763179}}
